Ernesto Carrella

Targeting

A very quick demo. We already had fishers being pushed by policies or prices to target only those areas where the profitable species live. It might be however that for exogenous reasons (perhaps fixed contracts with processors) fishers might want to target only specific species: this can be done indirectly through prices or directly by changing fishers’ utility function.

Red fish is the target, red fish is only available north hence fishers go north:

Easy application of the usual model where only the utility function is changed.
